high_descs: walk to face the round garbage bin to the left of the counter
pick up the brown egg from the bin
walk to face the microwave above the sinks
cook the egg in the microwave, remove egg from microwave
walk over to face the fridge
put the egg into the fridge
anns.task_desc: put a cooked egg into the fridge

high_descs: Turn around and face the trash can on the left.
Pick up the egg from inside the trash can.
Hold the egg and turn around. Move forward, and turn right to face the sink.
Open the microwave above the sink and place the egg inside. Shut the door then open it again. Take out the egg and shut the door.
Hold the egg and turn around, then right to face the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the egg inside. Shut the door.
Turn around and walk to the waste basket to your left next to the counter.
Pick up the egg inside the waste basket.
Turn around and walk to the microwave to your right above the sink.
Place the egg on the plate inside the microwave, cook the egg and remove it.
Turn around and walk to the fridge to your right.
Place the cooked egg inside the fridge for storage.
anns.task_desc: Place a cooked egg inside the fridge.
